import * as types from '../types'
import moment from 'moment'
const initalState = {
    Name: "",
    SSID: "",
    BirdDay: moment().format("MMM Do YY"),
    PostId: "",
    post: {},
    loadding: false,
    error: null
}
export const postReducer = (state = initalState,action) => {
    switch (action.type) {
        case types.UPDATE_NAME:
            return {
                ...state,
                Name: action.payload,
                SSID: action.ssid,
                PostId: action.post,
                BirdDay: moment(action.bird).format("MMM Do YY"),
                loading: false,
                error: null
            }
            default:
                return state
    }
}
